<h1 style="background-color:crimson;font-family:lucida grande,monospace;text-align:center;color:white;"">Serenity (Collaborative Project) 2024</h1>
<p style="font-family:lucida grande,monospace;color:white;text-align:center;">A collaborative piece made with my peer, Ashlyn Larrus, who is a 2D digital artist. 2D and 3D incorporation we did of a room comparing and contrasting how 3D differs from 2D.</p>
<p style="font-family:lucida grande,monospace;color:white;text-align:center;"> For this project, we wanted to express feelings of calmness, relaxation, and chill vibes by fitting it all in a single room.</p>
